Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.58,0:00:03.76,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)}阿扎帝斯坦王國 首都
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.31,0:00:07.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由一小部分軍人發動的政變已被平定
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.87,0:00:10.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但在城市裡 恐怖分子的襲擊仍在持續
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.35,0:00:16.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請各位國民千萬不要外出 呆在家裡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.93,0:00:24.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是阿扎帝斯坦第一公主 瑪麗娜·伊斯瑪依露
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.61,0:00:27.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請大家務必保持鎮定
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.66,0:00:29.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這塊真神給與的契約之地上
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.90,0:00:32.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,國民卻互相傷害對方
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.26,0:00:34.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是絕對不能容忍的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.85,0:00:41.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是因為改革派帶來了聯合國那些傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.02,0:00:51.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗娜殿下 願神保佑…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.52,0:00:55.42,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,0)}阿扎帝斯坦王國 王宮
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.51,0:00:59.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒找到拉瑟·馬蘇德·拉夫瑪迪嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.93,0:01:02.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在和UNION軍共同努力搜尋
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.25,0:01:05.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是似乎還需要很多時間
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.02,0:01:08.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.94,0:01:10.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在狀況真是糟透了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.22,0:01:15.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接收天線被摧毀 聯合國的技術人員們也撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.04,0:01:20.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且連天行者也來武裝干涉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.02,0:01:25.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要打破目前的僵局
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.38,0:01:28.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能通過保護拉瑟·馬蘇德·拉夫瑪迪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.46,0:01:29.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.00,0:03:10.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在阿扎帝斯坦王國
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.57,0:03:14.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宗教指導者拉瑟·馬蘇德·拉夫瑪迪被綁架
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.52,0:03:16.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以此為導火索 內亂爆發了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.37,0:03:20.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這場內亂發展到軍事政變的階段時
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.50,0:03:25.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天行者斷然由Gundam進行武裝干涉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.76,0:03:29.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在戰術預報士斯米拉琪·李·諾莉艾卡不在的情況下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.91,0:03:33.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剎那·F·塞艾和洛克昂·斯特拉特斯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.25,0:03:37.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能使阿扎帝斯坦的內亂停止下來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.48,0:03:45.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第三勢力？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.27,0:03:49.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除接受阿扎帝斯坦懇求的UNION
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.44,0:03:52.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和進行武裝干涉的我們之外
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.92,0:03:55.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有一股挑起內戰的勢力存在
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.50,0:03:59.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是說那股勢力綁架了拉瑟·馬蘇德·拉夫瑪迪嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.18,0:04:00.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說是我無端的推測
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.15,0:04:03.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但維達也暗示過這種可能性吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.38,0:04:05.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的證據呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.09,0:04:10.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在接收天線的建設現場
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.45,0:04:12.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遭到了遠距離的導彈攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.25,0:04:16.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從火力來看 使用MS的可能性很高
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.16,0:04:19.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使用MS的組織
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.47,0:04:22.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是出於什麼目的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.63,0:04:23.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.03,0:04:26.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我讓剎那去查這件事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.82,0:04:29.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這個國家 我們太引人注目了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.64,0:04:38.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根據洛克昂的情報 應該是在這附近發射過導彈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.54,0:04:42.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殘留反應
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.52,0:04:44.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來這裡確實出現過MS
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.21,0:04:46.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是在哪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.40,0:04:58.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,UNION？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.68,0:05:00.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回收的小艇也是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.61,0:05:03.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從這個反應來看 果然沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.72,0:05:06.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們也在搜查這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.29,0:05:09.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,PMC托拉斯的說法是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.33,0:05:13.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在摩洛裡亞的戰亂中已經失落…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.60,0:05:15.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.73,0:05:17.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偷聽可不好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.92,0:05:19.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被發現了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.18,0:05:21.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.50,0:05:28.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當地的孩子麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.95,0:05:29.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.02,0:05:35.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 我聽說這附近有戰鬥 所以就…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.55,0:05:36.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.94,0:05:40.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這個年齡對這樣的事情抱有興趣我也理解
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.96,0:05:43.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這附近還是很危險的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.34,0:05:45.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕快離開這裡比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.52,0:05:47.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 這就離開
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.57,0:05:48.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.83,0:05:54.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少年
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.10,0:05:58.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼看待這個國家的內亂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.23,0:06:01.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古拉哈姆
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.59,0:06:05.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼看待這個國家的內亂呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.19,0:06:07.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 我覺得…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.38,0:06:10.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能客觀地考慮嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.19,0:06:12.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話 你支持哪一邊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.24,0:06:14.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰也不支持
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.19,0:06:17.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪邊都有對的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.38,0:06:21.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是在這個戰鬥中 不斷有人死去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.97,0:06:25.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有很多人死去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.47,0:06:26.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同感啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.43,0:06:29.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為軍人 你也這麼說嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.56,0:06:32.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對於來到這個國家的我們 不歡迎麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.84,0:06:37.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為那麼多軍人來了的話 受害者也會增加
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.14,0:06:39.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不也是在戰鬥麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.95,0:06:43.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背後藏著的是什麼東西呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.95,0:06:49.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怖的臉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.74,0:07:04.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,片桐 前天從這裡攻擊接收天線的似乎是AEU的最新兵器Enact啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.75,0:07:05.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼突然…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.85,0:07:10.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且這台機體似乎是從摩洛利亞的PMC那裡奪走的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.12,0:07:12.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收隊了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.74,0:07:18.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古拉哈姆 為什麼要說那件事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.56,0:07:23.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 為什麼呢 就當是說漏了嘴好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.62,0:07:29.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,PMC的Enact…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.89,0:07:30.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.79,0:07:43.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個傢伙 那個男人 居然也和這場內亂有關
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.01,0:07:46.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.19,0:07:49.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.54,0:07:52.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼到了現在…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.10,0:08:04.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是恐怖襲擊麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.13,0:08:06.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據說這一帶改革派比較多
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.78,0:08:12.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MS派不上用場 只能請求出動對人制壓用機器人了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.46,0:08:16.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒用的 我方是以Gundam為目標才會派遣軍隊的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.94,0:08:19.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上面也不會分派出多餘的戰力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.81,0:08:21.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日子真難過啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.09,0:08:36.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗娜殿下…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.61,0:08:39.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,願神保佑…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.83,0:08:41.56,Second,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請大家務必保持鎮定 在這塊真神給與的契約之地上…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.53,0:08:49.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是何等的無力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.96,0:08:56.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.34,0:08:59.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.64,0:09:02.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去死吧 改革派的頭領
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.31,0:09:20.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.51,0:09:24.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.07,0:09:31.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我們要被人們這樣仇恨呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.61,0:09:34.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.73,0:09:36.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,F點3987
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.11,0:09:38.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裡有什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.61,0:09:42.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也可能什麼也沒有 但有這個可能性
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.71,0:09:44.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總比坐著乾等強吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.14,0:09:46.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了 剎那
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.22,0:09:49.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能讓紅龍一起去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.55,0:09:53.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在救重要人物的時候很有用哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.42,0:09:59.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GN系統休眠狀態解除
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.87,0:10:02.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優先權交給剎那·F·塞艾
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.77,0:10:05.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外裝甲迷彩層解除
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.07,0:10:10.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保持GN粒子散佈狀態 轉入戰鬥模式
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.78,0:10:22.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Exia 任務開始
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.94,0:10:35.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備好了嗎 紅龍
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.47,0:10:36.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.69,0:10:37.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.10,0:10:40.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dynames 前往目標
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.85,0:10:50.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.19,0:10:54.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個老頭 別說吃飯了 水都不喝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.68,0:10:56.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別管他
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.29,0:10:59.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想接受敵人的施捨麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.91,0:11:03.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 這個國家的人都是些不知變通的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.02,0:11:10.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天行者那幫人也來攪局 計劃都被打亂了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.28,0:11:12.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.89,0:11:14.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有機影正在接近這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.08,0:11:16.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是UNION的偵查嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.59,0:11:17.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.95,0:11:21.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那台白色的MS
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.00,0:11:24.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是Gundam嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.89,0:11:35.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Exia 到達目標地點
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.83,0:11:42.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是在這裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.93,0:11:53.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MS
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.76,0:11:57.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在這裡對付Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.79,0:11:59.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們帶老頭子逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.84,0:12:00.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.96,0:12:04.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那架Enact
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.21,0:12:06.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那架Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.99,0:12:10.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此 機師果然就是庫魯吉斯那個
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.94,0:12:14.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話 知道這個隱藏據點也在情理之中
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.51,0:12:24.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真沒想到 那時候的小屁孩居然坐上了Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.57,0:12:27.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的戰鬥還沒有結束嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.11,0:12:28.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鬼頭
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.16,0:12:31.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,庫魯吉斯都毀滅了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.82,0:12:36.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我當然知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.10,0:12:46.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為什麼會在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.49,0:12:49.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的神在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.70,0:12:52.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.93,0:12:54.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可沒義務回答你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.79,0:13:08.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太浪費了 這機體還是讓給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.51,0:13:10.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何啊 Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.04,0:13:12.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰會
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.10,0:13:17.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被這小子擺了一道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.78,0:13:18.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.11,0:13:22.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切按計劃進行中
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.06,0:13:27.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可未必
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.86,0:13:33.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.35,0:13:36.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.35,0:13:41.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隊長 敵襲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.30,0:13:44.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒反應
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.44,0:13:45.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.50,0:13:48.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該死
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.36,0:13:56.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.66,0:14:02.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別動
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.17,0:14:05.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請把那位先生交還給我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.30,0:14:18.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來這手臂還沒生銹
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.28,0:14:21.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.40,0:14:23.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天行者
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.36,0:14:25.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天行者？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.51,0:14:30.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,針對阿扎帝斯坦內戰進行武力干涉的私設武裝組織
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.40,0:14:34.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣 你們
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.54,0:14:50.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請乘上來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.05,0:14:51.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.40,0:15:03.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後任務 確認收到了 斯米拉琪小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.35,0:15:07.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼作戰
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.41,0:15:09.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的發出那樣的指示了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.06,0:15:11.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍有差錯的話Exia就
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.02,0:15:14.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是最可靠的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.37,0:15:15.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.54,0:15:17.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我贊成斯米拉琪小姐的計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.92,0:15:18.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.34,0:15:25.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有必要向世界展示 天行者組織的思想
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.97,0:15:31.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗娜殿下 天行者組織發來了消息
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.37,0:15:33.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天行者組織發來的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.27,0:15:36.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬蘇德·拉夫瑪迪被保護 正向王宮行進
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.63,0:15:39.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望王女準備早期停戰的會議
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.91,0:15:40.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.39,0:15:47.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解了 準備召開緊急會談
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.34,0:15:48.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,領命
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.34,0:15:52.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗娜殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.97,0:15:59.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我雖然無法認同他們的所作所為 也有可能是圈套
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.51,0:16:03.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我更想信任他們
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.50,0:16:06.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信任他們
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.02,0:16:15.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天行者組織正向王宮行進 這是真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.02,0:16:17.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且還帶著人質
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.93,0:16:20.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是那樣的話這可是最佳的機會 中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.49,0:16:25.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我拭目以待吧 Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.58,0:16:29.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是阿扎帝斯坦王宮前
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.08,0:16:35.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,市民們聽說了馬蘇德·拉夫瑪迪被保護 正向王宮行進的謠傳
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.46,0:16:38.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陸續地集中到這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.64,0:16:44.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據未確認情報顯示 保護馬蘇德·拉夫瑪迪的是天行者組織
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.29,0:16:48.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam究竟會不會出現
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.75,0:16:57.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之 代表著改革派的瑪麗娜·伊斯瑪依露王女 以及保守派的宗教指導者卡達夫氏之間的會談如果能實現
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.47,0:17:02.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿扎帝斯坦幾乎一定會朝著停止內戰的方向發展
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.06,0:17:06.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam會來的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.44,0:17:11.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別再粘著沙慈了啦 媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.29,0:17:17.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.16,0:17:18.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.12,0:17:20.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.49,0:17:22.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.48,0:17:31.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.99,0:17:34.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam從上空降下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.43,0:17:36.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害 真的來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.34,0:17:39.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.91,0:17:46.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在 Gundam緩緩地在王宮前著陸了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.63,0:17:50.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然解除了武裝!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.43,0:17:51.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太荒唐了!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.46,0:17:53.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非武裝狀態下就來到這裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.61,0:17:55.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要攻擊Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.53,0:17:56.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但…但是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.53,0:17:57.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是命令
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.47,0:18:01.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按照約定來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.51,0:18:02.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是槍擊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.72,0:18:05.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,數名市民正向著Gundam進行槍擊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.93,0:18:06.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.34,0:18:08.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快看 沙慈
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.86,0:18:13.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam開始移動了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.77,0:18:14.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢慢地朝向王宮
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.02,0:18:16.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正一步一步前進
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.30,0:18:21.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,釋放正保護的人質
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.62,0:18:22.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重複
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.72,0:18:25.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,釋放正保護的人質
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.52,0:18:26.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.28,0:18:27.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴看著
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.39,0:18:35.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.50,0:18:41.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.70,0:18:42.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗娜大人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.08,0:18:50.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.07,0:19:03.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.88,0:19:11.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成為Gundam…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.88,0:19:41.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請去王宮
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.30,0:19:44.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐在上面不怎麼舒服呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.28,0:19:46.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萬分抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.85,0:19:49.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請容我致謝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.17,0:19:50.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請快些
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.15,0:19:58.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是馬蘇德·拉夫瑪迪氏
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.87,0:20:01.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天行者組織保護了拉夫瑪迪氏
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.24,0:20:02.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並移送到了王宮
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.26,0:20:08.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.16,0:20:09.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危險啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.13,0:20:12.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剎那·F·塞艾
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.03,0:20:15.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.79,0:20:17.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是你麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.32,0:20:20.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗娜·伊斯瑪依露
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.33,0:20:22.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來會如何
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.09,0:20:25.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是否還會前來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.88,0:20:28.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剎那…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.49,0:20:30.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去戰鬥吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.10,0:20:33.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了你所相信的神明
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.65,0:20:35.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剎那
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.61,0:20:44.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中尉 追上去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.12,0:20:45.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在的話就能把Gundam…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.46,0:20:47.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能做那種事嗎?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.29,0:20:49.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是做了那種事情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.28,0:20:52.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們會被世界嗤之以鼻的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.08,0:20:59.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呼 還真是提心吊膽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.87,0:21:02.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是啊 大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.61,0:21:05.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就能解決這個問題了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.04,0:21:07.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解決不了的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.16,0:21:11.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 人們為了不再爭鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.14,0:21:13.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能夠相互讓步
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.01,0:21:16.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相互讓步…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.88,0:21:29.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬蘇德·拉夫瑪迪宣稱
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.40,0:21:32.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誘拐的主謀組織是傭兵部隊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.76,0:21:35.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是一場有人策劃的內亂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.11,0:21:41.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑幕很有可能是想要阻止阿扎帝斯坦現代化的勢力
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.69,0:21:44.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但並沒有發表犯罪聲明
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.41,0:21:46.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.43,0:21:50.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗娜·伊斯瑪依露 與 馬蘇德·拉夫瑪迪發表了共同聲明
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.44,0:21:55.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,號召國民停止內戰以及恐怖活動
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.66,0:21:58.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 阿扎帝斯坦的內亂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.67,0:22:00.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在仍持續著
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.68,0:23:35.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由四大國家群體正規軍進行的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.14,0:23:37.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聯合演習引發的紛爭
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.10,0:23:41.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機師們胸中沉浮之物
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.16,0:23:44.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回 決意的黎明
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.79,0:23:47.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若為Gundam 則…



